# ${b0}⠀⠀⢠⣿⣿⠃⠀⠒⠲⢶⣿⣿⣿⡄⠀ ⠀${lc}SHELL:     ${ic}${shell}${reset}
# ${b0}⠀⠠⠿⠿⠃⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠻⣿⣿⡀ ⠀${lc}${uitype}:        ${ic}${ui}${reset}

# EOF

# cat <<EOF

# ${g0} ⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⠀⣿⣿⣿⣿  ${nc}${USER}${ic}@${nc}${host}${reset}
# ${g0} ⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⠀⣿⣿⣿⣿  ${lc}OS:        ${ic}Manjaro${reset}
# ${g0} ⣿⣿⣿⣿⠀⣤⣤⣤⣤⠀⣿⣿⣿⣿  ${lc}KERNEL:    ${ic}${kernel}${reset} 
# ${g0} ⣿⣿⣿⣿⠀⣿⣿⣿⣿⠀⣿⣿⣿⣿  ${lc}UPTIME:    ${ic}${uptime}${reset}
