# EOF

# cat <<EOF

# ${y0}⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢴⡦⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀   ${nc}${USER}${ic}@${nc}${host}${reset}    ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
# ${g0}⠀⠀⠀⣿⢟⢵⣿${y0}⢸⡇${m0}⣿⡮⡻⣿   ⠀${lc}OS:        ${ic}$(cat /etc/centos-release | sed 's/release //')${reset}        ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
# ${g0}⠀⠀⠀⣵⣷⣕⢝${y0}⢸⡇${m0}⡫⣪⣾⣮   ⠀${lc}KERNEL:    ${ic}${kernel}${reset}    ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
# ${m0}⠀⠰⡷⣶⣶⣶⡶${b0}⠀⠀⠶⣶⣶⣶⢾⠆⠀⠀${lc}UPTIME:    ${ic}${uptime}${reset}    ⠀
